{"id": 1190, "genre": 1001, "title": "在工作场合，你觉得什么样子的打扮是无法被接受的？", "description": "到底是来上班还是来时装秀的啦！（题图来自：Scott Campbell）", "record_count": 4527, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160906163446NqmBwMLuh6489OQb.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-06T03:00:50Z", "options": [{"id": 113664, "content": "邋里邋遢", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747923}, {"id": 113665, "content": "超短裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460090}, {"id": 113666, "content": "皮带上的钥匙扣…想死的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747574}, {"id": 113667, "content": "干净整洁即可，别穿得跟下楼去超市买东西似的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676353}, {"id": 113668, "content": "小背心，沙滩裤，人字拖", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534828}, {"id": 113924, "content": "只要人干净，穿什么都可以接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467305}, {"id": 113669, "content": "人字拖", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512372}, {"id": 113925, "content": "黑眼圈的", "image": "img/option/option/20160907132616ytCFVETIc5UvL3wa.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505382}, {"id": 113670, "content": "杀马特", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747100}, {"id": 113671, "content": "裸体", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743796}, {"id": 113672, "content": "太骚气的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733459}, {"id": 115720, "content": "女的臭。男的露。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733067}, {"id": 113673, "content": "香港脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739238}, {"id": 113674, "content": "长得好看的怎么穿喔都欣赏 长得丑的就不该招进来好么！！！！ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120024}, {"id": 113675, "content": "抬手就见黑森林", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747951}, {"id": 163852, "content": "美，怎样都接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 113676, "content": "蓝头发绿头发黄头发彩头发一律再见…", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226639}, {"id": 113677, "content": "女士穿无袖露腋毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383674}, {"id": 113678, "content": "！！不洗头！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 196, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530280}, {"id": 113679, "content": "Cosplay…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198685}, {"id": 113680, "content": "所有在海边穿的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68042}, {"id": 117008, "content": "台客装，脖子上挂金链", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760899}, {"id": 113681, "content": "丝袜有洞或者拉丝……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747975}, {"id": 113682, "content": "乱发，无袖，拖鞋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747974}, {"id": 113683, "content": "身上有味道，说话声音超大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303725}, {"id": 113684, "content": "黑丝配象腿，热裤配象腿，短裙配象腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709676}, {"id": 113685, "content": "起毛球的各种衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744057}, {"id": 113686, "content": "破洞裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743821}, {"id": 113687, "content": "大立领polo，跟包皮过长一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449558}, {"id": 113688, "content": "丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746745}, {"id": 113689, "content": "满嘴大蒜儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747998}, {"id": 113945, "content": "皮带快束到胸口了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701868}, {"id": 113690, "content": "暴露各种异味", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543971}, {"id": 113691, "content": "那个说纹身穿孔的，耳洞怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737179}, {"id": 113692, "content": "头发油油的，穿牛仔裤+波鞋的装扮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748005}, {"id": 113693, "content": "衣服上很多洞", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748005}, {"id": 113694, "content": "超短裙短裤～露背露胸露腰～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748019}, {"id": 114718, "content": "游泳健身請問需要瞭解一下嗎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 61731}, {"id": 113695, "content": "头皮屑满天飞", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748023}, {"id": 113696, "content": "真的没有人觉得低腰裤这种东西很可怕么??", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731172}, {"id": 113697, "content": "很明显的肉色丝袜", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285575}, {"id": 113698, "content": "暴露", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747961}, {"id": 113699, "content": "穿运动鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711323}, {"id": 113700, "content": "风骚透视装，穿不穿两可的度假装，亮片超短裙什么的拜托都不是职场该穿的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748039}, {"id": 122916, "content": "搭配自身。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790633}, {"id": 113701, "content": "穿啥是个人的事情，关键是要干净得体", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682793}, {"id": 121637, "content": "紧身爆乳 半颗那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783519}, {"id": 113702, "content": "楼下互联网公司的男生拖鞋短裤，女生的露肩装热裤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256207}, {"id": 113703, "content": "对面的同事穿粉色?内衣套白色韩版透视装…每次工作交流都分心。每次都要去洗手间冷水洗脸，好压住我的小鹿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281714}, {"id": 113704, "content": "过于暴露，无论男女！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702911}]}